abstract: China defeats Algeria in women's volleyball World Cup in Matsumoto, Japan.
lead_paragraph: China assumed early control of the women’s volleyball World Cup in Matsumoto, Japan, beating Algeria in straight sets.

headline.main: Chinese Women Dominate at Volleyball World Cup
headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Volleyball; Chinese Women Dominate
